      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 when boundary conditions are matched directly to experimental conditions without extrapolation.",
      "rationale": "Simulation boundary conditions are set to match reported experimental values without extrapolation. Formal equivalency mapping between validation and COU parameter spaces is a MRL 3 requirement and is not assessed here."
